### Quantumy Auth API（VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP Client 用）
@base = http://localhost:3000

### 登録
POST {{base}}/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "reader@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "display_name": "テスト読者"
}

### ログイン
POST {{base}}/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "reader@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}
